short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 记录分析用户在搜索引擎上的搜索历史

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 不仅可以记录谷歌、百度等搜索引擎的搜所结果，也可以记录知乎等网站搜索框的结果，有利于知识的沉淀，避免重复多次搜索相同的事情。Not only can it record the search results of search engines like Google and Baidu, but it can also record the results from search boxes on websites like Zhihu, which is beneficial for the accumulation of knowledge and helps avoid repeatedly searching for the same things.
